cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.MM 

The paper discusses the computer vision task of Multiple Object Tracking (MOT), which involves tracking multiple objects in a video sequence. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses various approaches and techniques used in MOT, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses the evaluation of MOT systems, which could place it in the sub-category of cs.RO (Robotics and Control). Finally, the paper mentions the commercial potential of MOT, which could suggest that it belongs to cs.MM (Multimedia).
